\subsection{Participants}
For Study 1, 327 participants (Mean Age = 23.75, SD= 4.13, Range= 18 - 35, Gender: 216 male, 107 female, 3 non-binary, 1 prefer not to say) were recruited on Prolific.
For Study 2, 51 participants (Mean Age = 20.04, SD=1.99, Range=18-25, Gender: 13 male, 37 female) through an online recruitment tool for students at our university. All participants were Instagram users and had consumed alcohol in the past. AUDIT scores ranged from 1 to 25 (Mean = 8.18, SD = 4.95).






